                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing bismuth vanadate nanoparticles by oxidation ultrasonic precipitation method",
                    "一种氧化超声沉淀法制备钒酸铋纳米颗粒的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a method for preparing bismuth vanadate nano-particles by an oxidation ultrasonic precipitation method, which comprises the following steps: dissolving bismuth nitrate with a certain concentration in pure water or absolute ethyl alcohol under ultrasonic, adding a surfactant, continuing ultrasonic treatment until the bismuth nitrate is dissolved, adding vanadium trichloride with a certain concentration and hydrogen peroxide, and performing ultrasonic co-precipitation reaction to obtain bismuth vanadate nano-particles; and finally, centrifuging and drying to obtain the bismuth vanadate nanoparticles. The bismuth vanadate nanoparticles smaller than 100 nm are prepared through an oxidation ultrasonic precipitation method, operation and equipment are simple, experiment conditions are mild, the synthesis period is short, energy consumption is low, and good application prospects are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种氧化超声沉淀法制备钒酸铋纳米颗粒的方法，制备方法包含以下步骤:将一定浓度的硝酸铋在超声下溶于纯水或无水乙醇，加入表面活性剂继续超声至溶解后，加入将一定浓度的三氯化钒、双氧水超声进行共沉淀反应，最后离心、干燥，得到钒酸铋纳米颗粒。本发明采用氧化超声沉淀法制备小于100nm的钒酸铋纳米颗粒，操作及设备简单、实验条件温和、合成周期短、能耗低，具有良好的应用前景。"
                }
            ]
